org.javimmutable.collections

Interface JImmutableRandomAccessList<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Superinterfaces:
    Cursorable<T>, Indexed<T>, Insertable<T>, InvariantCheckable, Iterable<T>, JImmutableList<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JImmutableBtreeList, JImmutableTreeList

    @Immutable
public interface JImmutableRandomAccessList<T>
extends JImmutableList<T>
    Extension of JImmutableList that allows insertion and deletion at arbitrary indexes within the list.
